1
00:00:20,289 --> 00:00:22,966
Ahoy, from the other end of the world.
啊嘿   这是一封来自世界另一端的信

2
00:00:22,972 --> 00:00:25,120
Today, I grew a lot,
今天我长大了不少

3
00:00:25,163 --> 00:00:28,356
just like that, just because it was so hot.
因为这儿实在是太热了

4
00:00:28,424 --> 00:00:34,830
I'm sending you a measuring tape so you can see how much I've grown.
我给你们寄了一根卷尺好让你们看看我到底长了多少

5
00:00:35,975 --> 00:00:39,778
It all started when I came back from fishing at mid-day.
故事开始于中午   我钓完鱼回去

6
00:00:39,796 --> 00:00:42,412
It wasn't just the air that was hot,
不仅空气燥热

7
00:00:42,436 --> 00:00:44,036
but the ground, too.
连路面也烫脚 

8
00:00:44,066  --> 00:00:46,270
It's not made of ice here,
这儿的路不是冰做的

9
00:00:46,301 --> 00:00:48,381
but out of smooth rock.
竟然是光滑的石头